title: Grateful Dead Live at Alpine Valley Music Theatre on 1988-06-19

description:
Set I
Mississippi Half Step Uptown Toodleloo
Feel Like A Stranger

Comment
Kreutzmann gave a pep talk to the crowd before the show - be cool

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
